---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="SharePoint Services | Julius Bruch"
    description="SharePoint Online configuration, site design, and governance. Create modern collaboration spaces with Julius Bruch's SharePoint services."
>
    <main>
        <!-- Service Detail Section -->
        <section class="project-detail">
            <div class="container">
                <a href="/#services" class="back-link">
                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i>
                    <span data-en="Back to Services" data-de="Zurück zu Dienstleistungen">Back to Services</span>
                </a>

                <div class="project-detail-content">
                    <div class="project-detail-header">
                        <h1 data-en="SharePoint Services" data-de="SharePoint Services">SharePoint Services</h1>
                        <p class="project-category" data-en="Intranets | Document Management | Custom Lists" data-de="Intranets | Dokumentenmanagement | Benutzerdefinierte Listen">Intranets | Document Management | Custom Lists</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="project-detail-image">
                    <div class="image-placeholder" aria-hidden="true">📂</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="project-detail-body">
                        <h2 data-en="Service Overview" data-de="Leistungsübersicht">Service Overview</h2>
                        <p data-en="I help organize your content, implement best practices, and create modern collaboration spaces that empower your teams. From planning robust site architectures and managing permissions to configuring complex SharePoint lists that serve as fast, reliable data backends for your Power Apps." data-de="Ich helfe Ihnen, Ihre Inhalte zu organisieren, Best Practices zu implementieren und moderne Zusammenarbeitsbereiche zu schaffen, die Ihre Teams stärken. Von der Planung robuster Website-Architekturen und der Verwaltung von Berechtigungen bis hin zur Konfiguration komplexer SharePoint-Listen, die als schnelle, zuverlässige Daten-Backends für Ihre Power Apps dienen.">I help organize your content, implement best practices, and create modern collaboration spaces that empower your teams. From planning robust site architectures and managing permissions to configuring complex SharePoint lists that serve as fast, reliable data backends for your Power Apps.</p>
                        
                        <p data-en="Additionally, I create dedicated, highly structured SharePoint sites designed specifically as a secure foundation for your custom Power Apps. This ensures optimal performance and seamless integration. Comprehensive documentation is also provided to ensure your team can confidently manage the new environment." data-de="Zusätzlich erstelle ich dedizierte, hochstrukturierte SharePoint-Sites, die speziell als sichere Basis für Ihre individuellen Power Apps konzipiert sind. Dies gewährleistet optimale Leistung und nahtlose Integration. Umfassende Dokumentation wird ebenfalls bereitgestellt, um sicherzustellen, dass Ihr Team die neue Umgebung souverän verwalten kann.">Additionally, I create dedicated, highly structured SharePoint sites designed specifically as a secure foundation for your custom Power Apps. This ensures optimal performance and seamless integration. Comprehensive documentation is also provided to ensure your team can confidently manage the new environment.</p>

                        <h2 data-en="Licensing Information" data-de="Lizenzinformationen">Licensing Information</h2>
                        <p data-en="SharePoint Online is one of the most accessible platforms because it is already heavily seeded within the Microsoft 365 ecosystem:" data-de="SharePoint Online ist eine der zugänglichsten Plattformen, da sie bereits stark im Microsoft 365-Ökosystem verankert ist:">SharePoint Online is one of the most accessible platforms because it is already heavily seeded within the Microsoft 365 ecosystem:</p>
                        
                        <ul class="features-list">
                            <li data-en="Included in M365: Most Business Basic, Standard, Premium, and Enterprise (E3/E5) plans include full SharePoint Online access. You generally do not need to buy standalone SharePoint licenses for internal employees." data-de="In M365 enthalten: Die meisten Business Basic-, Standard-, Premium- und Enterprise-Pläne (E3/E5) beinhalten vollständigen Zugriff auf SharePoint Online. Sie müssen in der Regel keine eigenständigen SharePoint-Lizenzen für interne Mitarbeiter kaufen."><b>Included in M365:</b> Most Business Basic, Standard, Premium, and Enterprise (E3/E5) plans include full SharePoint Online access. You generally do not need to buy standalone SharePoint licenses for internal employees.</li>
                            
                            <li data-en="Storage Limits: A tenant typically receives 1 TB of base storage, plus 10 GB per licensed user. If your organization stores massive amounts of data, you may need to purchase 'Extra File Storage' add-ons." data-de="Speichergrenzen: Ein Tenant erhält typischerweise 1 TB Basisspeicher plus 10 GB pro lizenziertem Benutzer. Wenn Ihre Organisation riesige Datenmengen speichert, müssen Sie möglicherweise Add-ons für 'Zusätzlichen Dateispeicher' erwerben."><b>Storage Limits:</b> A tenant typically receives 1 TB of base storage, plus 10 GB per licensed user. If your organization stores massive amounts of data, you may need to purchase 'Extra File Storage' add-ons.</li>
                            
                            <li data-en="External Guests: Sharing SharePoint sites or documents with external clients or partners is usually free and covered under Microsoft's guest licensing models, making it a great portal for external collaboration." data-de="Externe Gäste: Das Teilen von SharePoint-Websites oder Dokumenten mit externen Kunden oder Partnern ist in der Regel kostenlos und durch die Gastlizenzierungsmodelle von Microsoft abgedeckt, was es zu einem großartigen Portal für externe Zusammenarbeit macht."><b>External Guests:</b> Sharing SharePoint sites or documents with external clients or partners is usually free and covered under Microsoft's guest licensing models, making it a great portal for external collaboration.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact CTA -->
        <section class="contact-cta">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 data-en="Need to organize your data?" data-de="Müssen Sie Ihre Daten organisieren?">Need to organize your data?</h2>
                <p data-en="Let's build an intranet and document management system that your team will actually love to use." data-de="Lassen Sie uns ein Intranet und ein Dokumentenmanagementsystem aufbauen, das Ihr Team wirklich gerne nutzen wird.">Let's build an intranet and document management system that your team will actually love to use.</p>
                <a href="/#contact" class="cta-button" data-en="Get in Touch" data-de="Kontaktieren Sie mich">Get in Touch</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>